<p><strong>For Mac &amp; iPhone users to make lists and stay organized. TaskPaper is a simple to-do list that&#8217;s surprisingly adept. Unlike standard organizers, TaskPaper gets out of your way so that you can get things done. Requires Mac OS X 10.5+ or iPhone OS 3.1+</strong></p>

